This example shows the compatibility of an Avango Classic fpHIDInput running
in the device daemon (av-daemon) to an instances of DeviceService and
DeviceSensor of the Avango NG framework.

Usage:

  1. Start Avango Classic Tracker:

     ~/old-avango/bin/./av-daemon.sh -f devices.scm

     NOTE: For parametrization look into the file.


  2. Start TestDevice using Avango NG instances:

     ./TestDevice

